es.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20and%20general%20secretary%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20those%20who%20doubt%20EVMs%20must%20demonstrate%20how%20they%20can%20be%20hacked.%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20who%20raise%20questions%20on%20EVM%2C%20if%20they%20have%20anything%2C%20they%20should%20go%20and%20show%20a%20demo%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20If%20work%20is%20done%20properly%20at%20the%20time%20of%20EVM%20randomisation%20and%20people%20properly%20work%20at%20the%20booths%20during%20mock%20polls%20and%20counting%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20any%20substance%20in%20this%20allegation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20still%20someone%20feels%20that%20EVMs%20can%20be%20hacked%2C%20then%20they%20should%20meet%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20show%20how%20EVMs%20can%20be%20hacked...%20Nothing%20can%20be%20done%20by%20just%20making%20random%20statements...%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Banerjee%2C%20Number%202%20in%20Trinamool%20after%20party%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Satish%20Chandra%20Dubey%20said%20the%20Trinamool%20leader%20has%20understood%20the%20truth%2C%20though%20late.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20elections%20happened%20recently%20--%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Jharkhand.%20The%20party%20that%20won%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20and%20no%20questions%20were%20raised%20regarding%20EVMs%20then.%20In%20Jharkhand%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20won%2C%20and%20there%20were%20no%20allegations.%20An%20alliance%20cannot%20sustain%20itself%20for%20long%20based%20on%20a%20lie.%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20may%20have%20realised%20this%20late%2C%20but%20at%20least%20he%20has%20understood%20the%20truth%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20several%20other%20Opposition%20parties%20raised%20questions%20about%20EVMs%20after%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%20po