ting%20in%20September%2C%20and%20they%20lowered%20rates%20again%20in%20November.%20As%20the%20Fed%20continues%20cutting%20rates%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20should%20go%20down.%20But%20they%20might%20not%20drop%20as%20much%20as%20initially%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20Low%20Will%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Go%3F%5C%22%3EHow%20Low%20Will%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Go%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20have%20been%20elevated%20this%20month%2C%20and%20we%20probably%20won't%20see%20them%20drop%20much%20this%20year.%20But%20depending%20on%20how%20the%20economy%20evolves%20in%202025%2C%20we%20should%20see%20them%20ease%20a%20bit%20next%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20are%20unlikely%20to%20drop%20back%20down%20to%20the%20historic%20lows%20of%202020%20and%202021%2C%20when%2030-year%20fixed%20rates%20fell%20below%203%25.%20But%20rates%20are%20expected%20to%20go%20down%20throughout%20the%20next%20year%20or%20two%2C%20and%20it's%20possible%20rates%20could%20eventually%20settle%20in%20closer%20to%206%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20I%20Refinance%20Now%20or%20Wait%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20I%20Refinance%20Now%20or%20Wait%20for%20Mortgage%20Rates%20To%20Drop%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20rates%20are%20lower%20now%2C%20some%20homeowners%20may%20be%20wondering%20if%20it's%20a%20good%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fwhen-to-refinance-mortgage%5C%22%3Etime%20to%20refinance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20high%20interest%20rate%20on%20your%20current%20mortgage%20and%20could%20save%20on%20your%20monthly%20payment%20by%20refinancing%20into%20a%20lower%20rate%2C%20it%20could%20be%20worth%20it%20to%20refinance%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fwill-mortgage-rates-go-down-this-year%5C%22%3Emortgage%20rates%20are%20expected%20to%20go%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20further%2C%20you%20might%20benefit%20from%20waiting%20to%20refinance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20it%20makes%20sense%20for%20you%20to%20refinance%20ultimately%20comes%20down%20to%20how%20much%20you'll%20pay%20to%20refinance%20and%20how%20much%20you%20can%20save%20on%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Faverage-mortgage-payment%5C%22%3Emortgage%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you%20save%20enough%20each%20month%20that%20you%20can%20recoup%20your%20out-of-pocket%20expenses%20relatively%20quickly%2C%20then%20refinancing%20may%20be%20worth%20it.%20You%20could%20also%20refinance%20now%20and%20then%20refinance%20again%20once%20rates%20drop%20further%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20depends%20on%20what%20makes%20sense%20for%20you%20financially.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20Do%20Mortgage%20Interest%20Rates%20Work%3F%5C%22%3EHow%20Do%20Mortgage%20Interest%20Rates%20Work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20mortgage%20interest%20rate%20is%20how%20much%20you'll%20pay%20to%20borrow%20money%20for%20a%20home%20purchase%20or%20refinance.%20Each%20month%2C%20you'll%20make%20a%20payment%20to%20pay%20back%20the%20funds%20you%20borrowed%2C%20and%20a%20portion%20of%20that%20payment%20will%20go%20toward%20paying%20the%20interest%20you%20owe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portion%20of%20your%20monthly%20payment%20that%20goes%20toward%20interest%20will%20go%20down%20over%20time%20through%20a%20process%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fmortgage-amortization-schedule%5C%22%3Eamortization%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20you%20pay%20off%20more%20of%20your%20mortgage%2C%20the%20loan%20balance%20is%20reduced%2C%20lowering%20your%20interest%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20say%20you%20get%20a%20mortgage%20of%20%24300%2C000%20with%20an%20interest%20rate%20of%206.5%25%20to%20buy%20a%20home.%20Every%20month%2C%20you'll%20pay%20about%20%241%2C896.%20On%20your%20very%20first%20mortgage%20payment%2C%20only%20%24271%20of%20that%20amount%20will%20go%20toward%20reducing%20your%20loan%20balance%2C%20while%20%241%2C625%20will%20be%20paid%20in%20interest.%20But%20if%20you%20fast%20forward%2020%20years%2C%20%24992%20of%20that%20same%20monthly%20payment%20will%20be%20applied%20to%20the%20loan%20balance%2C%20and%20about%20%24905%20will%20go%20toward%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20ask%20your%20lender%20for%20an%20amortization%20schedule%20to%20see%20the%20breakdown%20of%20your%20payments%20throughout%20the%20life%20of%20the%20loan%2C%20or%20you%20can%20use%20an%20online%20amortization%20calculator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20Often%20Do%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Change%3F%5C%22%3EHow%20Often%20Do%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Change%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20change%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20and%20they%20can%20fluctuate%20day-to-day%20or%20week-to-week%20based%20on%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20economy.%20If%20economic%20conditions%20are%20relatively%20stable%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20might%20not%20move%20much.%20But%20uncertainty%20or%20expectations%20that%20conditions%20will%20change%20soon%20can%20send%20rates%20up%20or%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20Shop%20for%20Mortgage%20Rates%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20Shop%20for%20Mortgage%20Rates%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%3EMortgage%20lenders%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20all%20offer%20the%20exact%20same%20rates%2C%20so%20you%20could%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20by%20shopping%20around%20for%20the%20best%20rate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20generally%20recommend%20getting%20quotes%20from%20a%20few%20different%20lenders%20%E2%80%94%20consider%20applying%20with%20at%20least%20three%20lenders%20to%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20the%20range%20of%20rates%20available%20to%20you.%20If%20you're%20still%20early%20in%20the%20process%2C%20you%20can%20apply%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fmortgage-preapproval%5C%22%3Epreapproval%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allows%20you%20to%20get%20an%20estimate%20of%20your%20rate%20while%20you're%20still%20searching%20for%20homes.%20If%20you're%20under%20contract%20on%20a%20home%2C%20you%20can%20apply%20for%20regular%20approval%2C%20which%20will%20give%20you%20a%20more%20accurate%20picture%20of%20what%20you'll%20pay%20with%20a%20given%20lender.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20sure%20to%20look%20at%20the%20overall%20offer.%20If%20you%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20lot%20in%20fees%20to%20get%20a%20lower%20rate%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20worth%20it.%20Also%20consider%20other%20benefits%20and%20features%20that%20are%20important%20to%20you%2C%20like%20if%20a%20lender%20has%20great%20customer%20service%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fdown-payment-assistance%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%20assistance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-monday-16-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734346803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F626bffc386fa90001905cc50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-monday-16-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20today's%20mortgage%20and%20refinance%20rates.%20Mortgage%20rates%20are%20up%20ahead%20of%20the%20coming%20Fed%20meeting%2C%20and%20they%20could%20fluctuate%20later%20this%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Molly%20Grace)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-monday-16-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Viral%20video%20of%20Alia-Neetu%20from%20RK's%20anniversary%20celebrations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734346733000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116367691%2Cimgsize-38122.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fviral-video-from-raj-kapoor-film-festival-sparks-speculation-over-neetu-kapoor-and-alia-bhatts-awkward-moment%2Farticleshow%2F116367691.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116367691.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Kapoor%20family%20celebrated%20Raj%20Kapoor's%20100th%20birth%20anniversary%20at%20the%20Raj%20Kapoor%20Film%20Festival%20in%20Mumbai.%20Ranbir%20honored%20his%20grandfather%20in%20a%20black%20bandhgala%2C%20while%20Alia%20dazzled%20in%20a%20floral%20Sabyasachi%20saree.%20A%20viral%20video%20showing%20an%20awkward%20moment%20between%20Alia%20and%20Neetu%20sparked%20speculation%20about%20family%20tension.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Who%20Really%20Benefits%20From%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F3vf0r6n_one-nation-one-election_640x480_10_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Cabinet%20has%20cleared%20the%20%E2%80%9COne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%9D%20(ONOE)%20Bill%20and%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20tabled%20in%20the%20ongoing%20winter%20session%20of%20Parliament.%20The%20party%20argues%20that%20ONOE%20will%20reduce%20cost%2C%20time%2C%20and%20energy%20spent%20on%20elections.%20However%2C%20the%20opposition%20views%20this%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20to%20nationalise%20state%20elections%2C%20thus%20enabling%20it%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20simultaneous%20polls.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20opposition's%20concerns%20stem%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20elections%20tend%20to%20mirror%20each%20other%20in%20states%20going%20for%20simultaneous%20elections.%20In%20four%20states%E2%80%94Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%94assembly%20elections%20were%20held%20alongside%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20April-June%202024.%20In%20all%20these%20states%2C%20the%20party%20that%20won%20the%20state%20elections%20also%20went%20on%20to%20win%20the%20majority%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%3A%20The%20NDA%E2%80%94the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Janasena%20Party%20(JSP)%E2%80%94won%20the%20state%20elections%20and%20swept%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20winning%2022%20out%20of%2025%20seats%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOdisha%3A%20The%20BJP%20won%20both%20the%20state%20elections%20and%20the%20maximum%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20(20%20out%20of%2021)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESikkim%3A%20The%20Sikkim%20Krantikari%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20won%20the%20state%20election%20and%20the%20only%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EArunachal%20Pradesh%3A%20The%20BJP%20won%20both%20the%20state%20elections%20and%20the%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20vote%20shares%20in%20both%20the%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20show%20a%20striking%20similarity%2C%20usually%20within%20a%20percentage-point%20range.%20The%20absolute%20number%20of%20votes%20also%20reflects%20this%20trend%3A%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20Odisha%2C%20the%20BJP%20secured%2045%25%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20and%2040%25%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20while%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20had%2040%25%20and%2038%25%2C%20respectively.%20In%20terms%20of%20absolute%20votes%2C%20the%20BJD%20secured%201.01%20crore%20votes%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%200.93%20crore%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20received%201%20crore%20and%201.13%20crore%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20NDA%20secured%2055%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20and%2054%25%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20(YSRCP)%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20garnered%2039%25%20and%2040%25%20votes%2C%20respectively.%20In%20absolute%20terms%2C%20the%20YSRCP%20received%201.33%20crore%20votes%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%201.32%20crore%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20while%20the%20NDA%20received%201.77%20crore%20and%201.78%20crore%20votes%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20earlier%20years%2C%20during%20simultaneous%20elections%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20similar%20trends%20had%20been%20observed.%20For%20example%2C%20in%202014%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20won%20both%20the%20state%20and%20general%20elections%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20TDP-BJP%20combine%20did%20so%20in%20Andhra%2C%20the%20Sikkim%20Democratic%20Front%20(SDF)%20in%20Sikkim%2C%20the%20BJD%20in%20Odisha%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20Arunachal.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20YSRCP%20won%20both%20the%20state%20and%20general%20elections%20in%20Andhra%2C%20the%20SKM%20in%20Sikkim%2C%20the%20BJD%20in%20Odisha%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20Arunachal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESplit%20Voting%20Is%20Rare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESplit%20voting%20refers%20to%20the%20phenomenon%20where%20voters%20choose%20different%20parties%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20as%20both%20elections%20are%20contested%20on%20different%20issues.%20This%20is%20seen%20in%20several%20states%20across%20India.%20For%20instance%2C%20voters%20in%20Delhi%20supported%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202014%20and%202019%20but%20chose%20AAP%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202015%20and%202020.%20However%2C%20many%20states%20do%20not%20exhibit%20such%20split%20voting%20patterns.%20Voters%20in%20states%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%20typically%20support%20the%20same%20party%20in%20both%20state%20and%20national%20elections.%20Maharashtra%2C%20however%2C%20bucked%20the%20trend%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20elections%20are%20held%20separately%2C%20voters%20perceive%20the%20state%20and%20national%20elections%20as%20distinct%2C%20and%20this%20separation%20allows%20them%20to%20treat%20each%20election%20differently.%20However%2C%20in%20states%20where%20simultaneous%20polls%20are%20held%2C%20there%20is%20little%20evidence%20of%20split%20voting.%20The%20trends%20from%20the%20recent%20polls%20in%20Andhra%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20and%20Arunachal%20suggest%20that%20simultaneous%20elections%20tend%20to%20reinforce%20the%20alignment%20between%20state%20and%20national%20voting%20patterns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEra%20Of%20Congress%20Dominance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneous%20elections%20were%20held%20from%201952%20to%201967%2C%20a%20period%20when%20the%20Congress%20dominated%20all%20through%2C%20except%20for%20intermittent%20periods%20in%20Kerala%20and%20Odisha.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20the%20Congress%20secured%20more%20than%20350%20seats%20in%20every%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20(1952%2C%201957%2C%20and%201962).%20This%20uniformity%20in%20results%20during%20the%20period%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%20raises%20the%20question%3A%20how%20did%20this%20dominance%20persist%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20led%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20had%20stalwart%20leaders%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20it%20also%20had%20very%20strong%20leadership%20in%20the%20states%2C%20coupled%20with%20minimal%20competition%20in%20the%20early%20years.%20Figures%20like%20Morarji%20Desai%20(Bombay)%2C%20Neelam%20Sanjeev%20Reddy%20(Andhra%20Pradesh)%2C%20Bidhan%20Chandra%20Roy%20(Bengal)%2C%20Govind%20Ballabh%20Pant%20(Uttar%20Pradesh)%2C%20K.%20Kamaraj%20(Madras)%2C%20Yashwantrao%20Chavan%20(Maharashtra)%2C%20and%20Shri%20Krishna%20Singh%20(Bihar)%20helped%20the%20Congress%20win%20state%20elections%20and%20secure%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20MPs%20from%20their%20respective%20states%20in%20national%20elections.%20The%20national%20election%20results%20were%20an%20aggregation%20of%20the%20state-level%20outcomes%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201967%20elections%20marked%20the%20end%20of%20an%20era%20in%20Indian%20politics%E2%80%94the%20era%20of%20Congress's%20unchallenged%20supremacy.%20The%20party%20failed%20to%20secure%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20eight%20of%20the%2016%20state%20elections%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20non-Congress%20governments.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20could%20not%20secure%20more%20than%20350%20seats%2C%20with%20its%20tally%20falling%20below%20300.%20Regional%20parties%20and%20breakaway%20groups%20began%20to%20erode%20the%20Congress's%20stronghold%20in%20several%20states%2C%20a%20trend%20that%20was%20also%20reflected%20in%20the%20national%20results.%20In%20states%20where%20the%20Congress%20lost%20power%2C%20it%20lost%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20well%2C%20bringing%20its%20total%20down%20to%20283.%20The%20Congress%20lost%20significant%20ground%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Madras%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Kerala%2C%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EAre%20The%20Fears%20Justified%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20trend%20of%20limited%20simultaneous%20polls%20in%20four%20states%2C%20alongside%20the%20historical%20data%20shows%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20mirroring%20between%20state%20and%20national%20results.%20So%2C%20is%20the%20fear%20of%20regional%20parties%20getting%20pushed%20to%20the%20margins%20justified%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201967%20results%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20limited%20simultaneous%20polls%20in%202014%2C%202019%20and%202024%2C%20show%20that%20the%20party%20that%20is%20stronger%20in%20states%E2%80%94whether%20national%20or%20regional%E2%80%94tends%20to%20benefit%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20as%20well%2C%20winning%20a%20higher%20number%20of%20seats.%20This%20is%20because%20split%20voting%20is%20not%20the%20norm%2C%20as%20demonstrated%20earlier.%20When%20split%20voting%20does%20occur%2C%20it%20is%20typically%20seen%20only%20in%20urban%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParties%20that%20are%20strong%20in%20states%20tend%20to%20benefit%2C%20as%20historical%20data%20suggests.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20not%20necessarily%20benefit%20from%20ONOE%2C%20as%20is%20often%20claimed.%20In%20fact%2C%20strong%20regional%20parties%20may%20stand%20to%20gain%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20than%20they%20would%20otherwise%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20about%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20where%20the%20contests%20are%20bipolar%2C%20with%20both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20having%20similar%20support%20bases%3F%20This%20remains%20a%20very%20difficult%20question%20to%20answer%20at%20this%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734346560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F3vf0r6n_one-nation-one-election_640x480_10_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2F