%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Man%20Mauled%20To%20Death%20By%20His%20XL%20Bully%20Dogs%20In%20Front%20Of%20Horrified%20Onlookers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20California%20man%C2%A0has%20died%20after%20being%20mauled%20to%20death%20by%20his%20three%20'XL%20bully'%20dogs%20at%20a%20children's%20playground.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F12%2F15%2Fus-news%2Fcalifornia-man-mauled-to-death-by-his-own-3-dogs-in-front-of-horrified-onlookers-at-playground%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20emergency%20calls%20were%20made%20to%20the%20San%20Diego%20police%20around%20noon%2C%20reporting%20a%20dog%20attack%20at%20the%20Mesa%20Viking%20Neighborhood%20Park.%20Upon%20arrival%2C%20officers%20found%20the%20victim%20being%20violently%20attacked%20by%20the%20three%20XL%20bullies.%20Despite%20desperate%20attempts%20by%20bystanders%20to%20intervene%2C%20the%20dogs%20refused%20to%20release%20their%20grip%20on%20the%20man.%20The%20ferocity%20of%20the%20attack%20was%20so%20severe%20that%20one%20witness%20initially%20believed%20police%20were%20attempting%20to%20subdue%20a%20violent%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20saw%20they%20had%20something%20trapped%20in%20the%20weeds%20over%20here.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20person%20at%20first%20because%20they%20were%20talking%20about%20setting%20up%20a%20perimeter.%20They%20were%20big%2C%20like%20XL%20bullies%2C%20just%20massive%20muscle%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20witness%20Steve%20Marto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20brutal%20attack%20continued%2C%20bystanders%20attempted%20to%20intervene%2C%20using%20shovels%20and%20a%20golf%20club%20to%20try%20and%20deter%20the%20dogs.%20However%2C%20the%20animals'%20ferocity%20persisted%2C%20forcing%20the%20police%20to%20resort%20to%20using%20tasers%20to%20subdue%20them.%20Two%20of%20the%20dogs%20were%20eventually%20caught%20and%20restrained%2C%20but%20a%20third%20managed%20to%20escape%20into%20the%20nearby%20neighbourhood.%20That%20prompted%20the%20nearby%20Ericson%20Elementary%20School%20to%20go%20into%20lockdown%20until%20the%20animal%20was%20found%20back%20at%20its%20home%20and%20captured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20search%20operation%20ensued%2C%20and%20the%20loose%20dog%20was%20eventually%20tracked%20back%20to%20its%20home%2C%20where%20it%20was%20safely%20captured.%20The%20community%20breathed%20a%20collective%20sigh%20of%20relief%20as%20the%20situation%20was%20brought%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20officer%20was%20able%20to%20break%20up%20the%20dogs.%20They%20fled%2C%20and%20the%20injured%20male%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20with%20unknown%20injuries%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20said.%20However%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20man%20identified%20as%20Pedro%20Luis%20Ortega%2C%20died%20at%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESan%20Diego%20Humane%20Society%2C%20along%20with%20police%2C%20confirmed%20the%20owner's%20death%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F12%2F15%2Fus%2Fdeadly-dog-attack-in-san-diego-leaves-one-dead-and-another-injured%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20victim%20sustained%20fatal%20injuries.%20Our%20hearts%20go%20out%20to%20the%20victim's%20family%20during%20this%20incredibly%20difficult%20time.%20Upon%20arrival%2C%20our%20Humane%20Officers%20worked%20closely%20with%20SDPD%20to%20locate%20two%20dogs%20that%20were%20still%20loose%20and%20safely%20impounded%20a%20third%20dog%20that%20had%20been%20secured%20in%20a%20vehicle%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Humane%20Society%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dogs%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20%26quot%3Bunder%20mandatory%20bite%20quarantine%20protocols%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20were%20later%20euthanised%20following%20standard%20protocol%2C%20the%20Humane%20Society%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Society%20officers%20also%20discovered%20a%20second%20person%20who%20had%20suffered%20severe%20bite%20wounds%20while%20attempting%20to%20aid%20the%20initial%20victim.%20This%20person%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20and%20is%20currently%20recovering.%20The%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fmmwr%2Fvolumes%2F72%2Fwr%2Fmm7236a6.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDuring%25202011%25E2%2580%25932021%252C%2520a%2520total%2C)%2520to%252081%2520(2021).%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22link%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fmmwr%2Fvolumes%2F72%2Fwr%2Fmm7236a6.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDuring%25202011%25E2%2580%25932021%252C%2520a%2520total%2C)%2520to%252081%2520(2021).%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereports%20that%20on%20average%20nationally%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2043%20people%20die%20from%20dog%20bites%20and%20attacks%20every%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734346080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F8ar18pog_xl-bully-dogs_625x300_05_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-mauled-to-death-by-his-own-xl-bully-dogs-in-front-of-horrified-onlookers-7260738%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20dogs%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20%26quot%3Bunder%20mandatory%20bite%20quarantine%20protocols%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20were%20later%20euthanised%20following%20standard%20protocol.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-mauled-to-death-by-his-own-xl-bully-dogs-in-front-of-horrified-onlookers-7260738%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Narayana%20Murthy%20reiterates%20on%2070%20hrs%20workweek%3A%20But%20what%20about%20employees'%20health%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734345699000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-1