3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20lesser-known%20stories%20that%20capture%20his%20life%20and%20legacy%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20He%20slept%20on%20train%20floors%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20early%20years%2C%20Ustad%20Zakir%20often%20travelled%20by%20train%20and%20when%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20seat%2C%20he%20slept%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20using%20newspapers%20as%20bedding.%20Despite%20the%20discomfort%2C%20he%20always%20kept%20his%20%3Cem%3Etabla%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20his%20lap%2C%20carefully%20protecting%20it%20from%20being%20touched%20or%20damaged.%20Even%20then%2C%20his%20respect%20for%20the%20instrument%20was%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20His%20love%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Etabla%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebegan%20at%20the%20age%20of%20seven%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUstad%20Zakir%20developed%20a%20deep%20interest%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Etabla%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20the%20tender%20age%20of%20seven.%20Under%20the%20strict%2C%20disciplined%20guidance%20of%20his%20father%2C%20the%20legendary%20Ustad%20Alla%20Rakha%2C%20he%20underwent%20rigorous%20training.%20By%20the%20time%20most%20children%20were%20just%20learning%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F382543%2Fvarijashree-venugopal-grammy-award-nomination-a-rock-somehwere-jacob-collier-anoushka-shankar-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eread%20music%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Zakir%20was%20already%20giving%20public%20performances%2C%20showcasing%20his%20early%20genius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_X6dGABw3_%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F