%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20said%20Monday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20GRAP-III%2C%20all%20schools%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20must%20switch%20to%20a%20hybrid%20class%20mode%20for%20students%20till%20Class%20V%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20restrictions%20on%20the%20entry%20of%20diesel-powered%20commercial%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20hybrid%20class%20mode%20means%20students%20and%20parents%20can%20choose%20between%20online%20and%20in-person%20classes%2C%20depending%20on%20availability%20of%20infrastructure%20like%20computers%20and%20the%20internet%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoods%20vehicles%20with%20engines%20below%20the%20BS-IV%20certification%20cannot%20run%2C%20except%20for%20those%20used%20for%20emergency%20purposes%20or%20to%20provide%20essential%20services%2C%20and%20goods%20carriers%20registered%20outside%20the%20national%20capital%20cannot%2C%20till%20further%20notice%2C%20enter%20the%20city%20if%20their%20engine%20is%20below%20the%20BS-IV%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20offices%20in%20Delhi%20and%20neighbouring%20states%20will%20stagger%20working%20hours%2C%20with%20the%20central%20government%20likely%20to%20implement%20a%20similar%20measure%20for%20its%20offices%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%202.30%20pm%20the%20city's%20AQI%20was%20366%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20higher%20end%20of%20the%20'very%20poor'%20category.%20This%20is%20a%20sharp%20spike%20from%20seven%20days%20ago%3B%20on%20December%207%20it%20233%2C%20which%20classified%20it%20as%20'moderate'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20three%20days%20before%20that%2C%20Delhi's%20AQI%20was%20at%20211.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20improvement%20in%20air%20quality%20meant%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20on%20December%205%2C%20allowed%20the%20CAQM%20to%20relax%20anti-pollution%20measures%20from%20GRAP-IV%2C%20the%20strictest%20of%20a%20four-stage%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20meant%20to%20tackle%20deteriorating%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20the%20air%20quality%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20surrounding%20areas%20was%20consistently%20in%20the%20'severe'%20and%20'very%20poor'%20category%2C%20prompting%20annual%20health%20warnings%20from%20medical%20professionals%20and%20triggering%20a%20rush%20of%20cases%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20asking%20for%20directions%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20several%20weeks%20a%20top%20court%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%20have%20held%20several%20hearings%20on%20the%20annual%20air%20quality%20crisis%2C%20looking%20at%20issues%20from%20farm%20fires%20(i.e.%2C%20farmers%20burning%20agricultural%20waste)%20to%20ineffective%20bans%20on%20polluting%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20court%20criticised%20the%20authorities%20for%20not%20following%20the%20law%3B%20for%20example%2C%20when%20GRAP-IV%20was%20in%20effect%2C%20the%20court%20slammed%20officials%20continuing%20to%20allow%20non-essential%20construction%20activities%20that%20are%20not%20permitted%20at%20that%20time.%20The%20court%20also%20had%20questions%20for%20the%20Delhi%20government%20for%20not%20stopping%20vehicles%20carrying%20non-essential%20goods%20from%20entering%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20questioned%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20the%20CAQM%2C%20a%20central%20government%20panel%2C%20for%20not%20ordering%20stricter%20anti-pollution%20measures%20once%20the%20AQI%20had%20crossed%20the%20300-mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20which%20hears%20cases%20and%20laments%20about%20Delhi's%20air%20quality%20every%20year%20-%20has%20been%20just%20as%20critical%20this%20year%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20post-Diwali%20deterioration%20that%20is%2C%20again%2C%20an%20annual%20and%20predictable%20worsening%20of%20AQI%20after%20many%20in%20the%20city%20flout%20the%20ban%20on%20firecrackers.%3C%2F