nt%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20collage%20including%20Dhruv%20Suyamprakasam%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6757604e91c1cc343d477c10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDhruv%20Suyamprakasam%20founded%20a%20startup%20and%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20twice%20to%20scale%20his%20company.%3Cp%3EHeadshot%20courtesy%20of%20Dhruv%20Suyamprakasam%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDhruv%20Suyamprakasam%20launched%20a%20telemedicine%20startup%20and%20initially%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBengaluru's%20fast-paced%20culture%20clashed%20with%20the%20healthcare%20industry's%20needs%20and%20the%20team%20moved%20back.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20that%20Bengaluru%20has%20its%20own%20merits%20and%20should%20not%20be%20compared%20to%20the%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Dhruv%20Suyamprakasam%2C%20a%20founder%20who%20launched%20his%20startup%20in%20Bengaluru%20but%20later%20moved%20out.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20father%20was%20a%20first-generation%20entrepreneur%20and%20ran%20a%20thriving%20business%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20in%20Coimbatore%2C%20a%20small%20city%20in%20Southern%20India.%20I%20would%20follow%20him%20on%20business%20trips%2C%20and%20growing%20up%2C%20I%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Hyderabad%2C%20two%20of%20India's%20biggest%20business%20hubs%20in%20the%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20mechanical%20engineering.%20During%20college%2C%20I%20became%20fascinated%20with%20entrepreneurship%20and%20building%20something%20of%20my%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20considered%20entering%20manufacturing%2C%20but%20I'd%20have%20to%20focus%20on%20making%20one%20product%20at%20a%20time.%20I%20decided%20building%20software%20was%20the%20answer%2C%20but%20I%20still%20didn't%20have%20an%20idea%20of%20exactly%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20software%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20I%20met%20my%20now-co-founder%2C%20a%20medical%20doctor%2C%20who%20was%20also%20my%20relative%2C%20at%20a%20wedding.%20We%20kept%20in%20touch%20and%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20our%20startup%20%E2%80%94%20a%20telemedicine%20company%20that%20would%20allow%20people%20to%20access%20doctors%20virtually%20and%20across%20local%20and%20international%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20recent%20graduate%20with%20a%20good%20job%20offer.%20My%20cofounder%20was%20worried%20about%20how%20our%20family%20would%20react%20to%20me%20quitting%20to%20venture%20out%20on%20my%20own.%20But%20I%20absconded%20the%20job%20offer%20and%20began%20working%20on%20our%20idea%20full%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208d5f415-4d64-464d-a7e5-eaf9b05e4082%5C%22%3EMoving%20to%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20brought%20on%20another%20cofounder%20who%20lived%20in%20Bengaluru%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20had%20read%20about%20the%20city%20being%20the%20center%20of%20the%20mainstream%20startup%20ecosystem.%20In%202010%2C%20moving%20to%20Bengaluru%20felt%20like%20the%20best%20decision%20for%20me%20as%20a%20founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20wasn't%20the%20best%20place%20for%20us.%20It's%20a%20place%20that%20expects%20companies%20to%20grow%20fast%20and%20fail%20fast.%20I%20didn't%20think%20it%20was%20the%20right%20pressure%20to%20put%20on%20a%20healthcare%20startup%2C%20which%20has%20no%20margin%20for%20errors%20and%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20trust%20from%20people.%20We%20met%20investors%20who%20had%20expectations%20like%20getting%20100%20paid%20consultations%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2012%20years%20back%2C%20I%20also%20felt%20like%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20bias%20from%20investors.%20I%20felt%20excluded%20because%20I%20didn't%20speak%20Hindi%2C%20which%20is%20the%20most%20spoken%20language%20in%20India%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20go%20to%20college%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20the%20most%20coveted%20engineering%20school%20in%20the%20country.%20I%20also%20got%20some%20judgment%20for%20being%20from%20a%20small%20town%20many%20people%20had%20not%20heard%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20combination%20of%20those%20factors%20helped%20us%20decide%20to%20move%20back%20to%20my%20hometown%20after%20around%2016%20months%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20challenges%20back%20home%2C%20too.%20We%20faced%20issues%20with%20our%20internet%20connection%2C%20which%20we%20never%20had%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20established%20startup%20community.%20But%20it%20gave%20us%20the%20space%20to%20grow%20at%20our%20own%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20we%20have%20onboarded%20about%204%2C500%20doctors%20to%20the%20platform%20and%20have%20patients%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20The%20company%20has%20grown%20to%20around%20200%20employees%2C%20and%20we%20have%20expanded%20to%20include%20health%20content%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223afe972b-8232-43b2-993e-d4f34155bde2%5C%22%3EHeart%20of%20India's%20startup%20scene%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20even%20moved%20back%20to%20Bengaluru%20for%20a%20second%20time%20in%202016%20because%20we%20had%20grown%20a%20lot%20more%20as%20a%20company%20and%20thought%20things%20might%20be%20different%20this%20time%20around.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20thought%20that%20maybe%20the%20first%20time%20around%2C%20we%20hadn't%20understood%20how%20Bengaluru%20worked%20and%20how%20things%20were%20done.%20We%20were%20ready%20to%20give%20it%20a%20second%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20inclusivity%20had%20improved%20because%20of%20the%20push%20for%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%2C%20but%20not%20much%20had%20changed%20for%20the%20healthcare%20industry%20like%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20we%20were%20expected%20to%20show%20results.%20We%20ended%20up%20coming%20back%20to%20my%20hometown%20after%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20has%20tons%20of%20advantages%2C%20like%20proximity%20to%20venture%20capital%2C%20a%20massive%20pool%20of%20tech%20talent%2C%20and%20more%20opportunities%20for%20networking%2C%20which%20can%20be%20helpful%20in%20the%20early%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20building%20a%20business%20outside%20the%20tech%20hub%20is%20also%20a%20good%20option%2C%20especially%20because%20of%20lower%20costs.%20While%20employee%20salaries%20are%20usually%20on%20par%2C%20founders%20can%20save%20a%20lot%20on%20office%20space%20and%20home%20rent%20if%20they%20build%20from%20smaller%20cities%20and%20travel%20to%20Bengaluru%20as%20needed.%20I%20also%20think%20we%20need%20more%20tech%20hubs%20in%20India%20outside%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e0ffe79-24f4-4f20-8b25-91753df1c9a0%5C%22%3EIt's%20no%20Silicon%20Valley%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20Bengaluru%20should%20be%20compared%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%20at%20all.%20Since%202018%2C%20I%20have%20also%20spent%20time%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20growing%20our%20business.%20Now%2C%20our%20company%20is%20headquartered%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20I%20spend%20four%20to%20five%20months%20of%20the%20year%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20has%20an%20amazing%20tech%20crowd%2C%20but%20Silicon%20Valley%20is%20Silicon%20Valley%20for%20a%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20people%20are%20far%20more%20open-minded%20and%20inclusive%20about%20giving%20opportunities%20to%20those%20from%20different%20backgrounds%2C%20which%20has%20allowed%20it%20to%20become%20a%20sponge.%20The%20city%20just%20sucks%20up%20anyone%20with%20talent%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20have%20made%20me%20incredibly%20happy%20if%20the%20first%20large%20language%20model%20came%20from%20India%2C%20but%20it%20didn't.%20It%20came%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20where%20Sam%20Altman's%20team%20was%20