g%20that%20gave%20me%20more%20enjoyment%20and%20provided%20additional%20income%20to%20avoid%20chipping%20away%20at%20all%20of%20my%20retirement%20savings%2C%20which%20I%20began%20saving%20for%20in%20my%20mid-40s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Taskrabbit%2C%20my%20other%20part-time%20jobs%20included%20stints%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-teaching-job-after-decades-now-work-at-costco-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECostco%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20customer%20service%20work%2C%20and%20driving%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20an%20article%20in%20my%20local%20newspaper%20about%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20had%20discovered%20Taskrabbit.%20It%20intrigued%20me%2C%20so%20I%20immediately%20went%20online%20to%20create%20a%20Tasker%20account%20and%20have%20them%20run%20a%20background%20check%20on%20me.%20That%20was%20completed%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days%2C%20and%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223c95a31-dcd3-42ad-b4b4-59fc6964ad79%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20now%20been%20Tasking%20for%203%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20enjoyed%20assembling%20things%2C%20but%20there%20was%20a%20learning%20curve.%20Although%20I%20had%20previously%20worked%20with%20Ikea%20furniture%2C%20there%20was%20much%20to%20figure%20out%20about%20some%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Btricks%26quot%3B%20associated%20with%20Ikea%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20over%20%2447%2C000%20in%202023%2C%20my%20highest%20year%20in%20earnings%20yet.%20I%20average%20%243%2C000%20to%20%245%2C000%20in%20earnings%20monthly.%20I%20could%20live%20on%20my%20retirement%20savings%20if%20I%20had%20to%2C%20but%20Taskrabbit%20income%20helps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22156b9a3a-1b9d-457d-948b-ab99f1f61266%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20do%20tasks%20almost%20daily%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20complete%20between%20one%20and%20three%20tasks%20daily%2C%20averaging%20about%20four%20to%20five%20days%20a%20week.%20Most