0Mistake%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nikita%20moved%20to%20a%20PG%20accommodation%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20her%20mother%20and%20brother%20hid%20in%20Jhusi%20town%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj%20district.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20they%20all%20communicated%20with%20relatives%20via%20WhatsApp%20calls.%20But%2C%20Nikita%20made%20one%20call%2C%20apparently%20by%20mistake%2C%20to%20one%20of%20her%20close%20relatives.%20Police%20tracked%20the%20tower%20location%20and%20reached%20the%20PG%20accommodation%20in%20Gurugram's%20Rail%20Vihar%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20She%20was%20detained%20and%20made%20to%20make%20a%20call%20to%20her%20mother.%20When%20Nisha%20Singhania%20received%20the%20call%2C%20police%20tracked%20them%20to%20Jhusi%20town%20and%20took%20them%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECops%20faced%20a%20big%20question.%20Where%20will%20Atul's%20four-year-old%20son%20stay%3F%20The%20child%20was%20entrusted%20to%20one%20of%20the%20family's%20relatives.%20The%20police%20recorded%20the%20accused's%20statements%20during%20the%20transit%20to%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Cautious%20Late-Night%20Flight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20said%20a%20key%20challenge%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20co-passengers%20did%20not%20recognise%20Nikita%20during%20the%20journey.%20The%20three%20were%20taken%20to%20Bengaluru%20on%20a%20late%20night%20flight.%20Police%20sources%20said%20they%20were%20extra%20cautious%20in%20ensuring%20that%20the%20news%20of%20their%20detention%20was%20not%20out%20before%20the%20team%20reached%20Bengaluru.%20This%20was%20because%20of%20the%20outrage%20sparked%20by%20Atul%20Subhash's%20death.%20Any%20news%20of%20Nikita%20and%20her%20family%20being%20taken%20to%20Bengaluru%20may%20have%20led%20to%20dangerous%20situations%20at%20the%20airport%20or%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Nikita%2C%20her%20mother%20Nisha%20and%20brother%20Anurag%20were%20taken%20for%20medical%20examination%20and%20then%20to%20the%20magistrate's%20residence%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20before%20being%20sent%20to%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Nikita%20Has%20Told%20Police%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20Nikita%20has%20said%20during%20interrogation%20that%20she%20never%20harassed%20Atul%20and%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20harassed%20by%20him.%20She%20also%20said%20that%20she%20wouldn't%20have%20left%20their%20home%20if%20she%20wanted%20money.%20Atul%20Subhash%2C%20in%20his%2024-page%20suicide%20note%20and%2080-minute%20video%2C%20has%20accused%20Nikita%20and%20her%20family%20of%20filing%20false%20cases%20of%20cruelty%20and%20dowry%20harassment%20against%20him%20and%20his%20family%20to%20extort%20money%20from%20them.%20He%20has%20said%20she%20had%20demanded%20a%20huge%20sum%20of%20Rs%203%20crore%20to%20settle%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Subhash%20was%20found%20dead%20last%20Monday%20at%20his%20Bengaluru%20residence.%20Following%20a%20complaint%20by%20his%20brother%20Bikas%20Kumar%2C%20police%20filed%20an%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20case.%20His%20family%20has%20also%20said%20they%20want%20custody%20of%20the%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20preliminary%20investigation%2C%20Atul%20had%20planned%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%2015%20days%20before%20his%20death.%20He%20had%20searched%20about%20legal%20issues%20on%20Google%20and%20written%20the%20note%20three%20days%20before%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734340020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fmepekvo_nikita-singhania_625x300_16_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fatul-subhash-suicide-case-nikita-singhania-bengaluru-techie-suicide-how-1-phone-call-helped-bengaluru-cops-track-down-nikita-singhania-family-7259828%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nikita%20Singhania%2C%20the%20estranged%20wife%20of%2034-year-old%20techie%20Atul%20Subhash%2C%20changed%20her%2