s%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc205wnvlqn6o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rescuers%20comb%20through%20the%20debris%20in%20the%20French%20Indian%20Ocean%20territory%20hit%20by%20the%20worst%20storm%20in%2090%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A598%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc205wnvlqn6o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc205wnvlqn6o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc205wnvlqn6o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bashar%20al-Assad%20Airlifted%20%24250%20Million%20Of%20Syria's%20Wealth%20To%20Moscow%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20regime%20of%20ousted%20Syrian%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad%20airlifted%20around%20%24250%20million%20(Rs%202%2C082%20crore)%20in%20cash%20to%20Moscow%2C%20according%20to%20a%20stunning%20revelation%20made%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%20The%20transactions%20were%20carried%20out%20in%20a%20two-year%20period%20-%202018%20and%202019%20-%20and%20included%20nearly%20two%20tonnes%20of%20%24100%20bills%20and%20currency%20notes%20of%20500%20euro%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%20These%20bank%20notes%20were%20flown%20to%20Moscow's%20Vnukovo%20airport%20and%20deposited%20in%20sanctioned%20Russian%20banks.%20The%20report%20also%20said%20that%20Assad's%20relatives%20were%20secretly%20buying%20assets%20in%20Russia%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-assads-ouster-nations-intensify-contact-efforts-with-new-syria-rulers-7257702%5C%22%3EAfter%20Assad's%20Ouster%2C%20Nations%20Intensify%20Contact%20Efforts%20With%20New%20Syria%20Rulers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F84ef8bdd-d070-431d-90f6-332937911096%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20these%20transactions%20show%20the%20extent%20Assad's%20regime%20went%20to%20bypass%20western%20sanctions%20that%20pushed%20it%20out%20of%20the%20financial%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssad%20fled%20Syria%20on%20December%208%20following%20an%2011-day%20rebel%20offensive%20led%20by%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS)%2C%20after%20years%20of%20civil%20war%20sparked%20by%20his%20violent%20crackdown%20on%20anti-government%20protests%20in%202011.%20He%20is%20now%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20has%20killed%20upwards%20of%20500%2C000%20people%20and%20displaced%20more%20than%20half%20the%20country's%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssad%20has%20faced%20criticism%20from%20several%20opposition%20figures%20who%20accuse%20his%20regime%20of%20looting%20Syria's%20wealth%20and%20turning%20to%20criminal%20activity%20to%20finance%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavid%20Schenker%2C%20former%20US%20Assistant%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20Near%20Eastern%20Affairs%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20transfers%20were%20not%20surprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20regime%20would%20have%20to%20bring%20their%20money%20abroad%20to%20a%20safe%20haven%20to%20be%20able%20to%20use%20it%20to%20procure%20the%20fine%20life...%20for%20the%20regime%20and%20its%20inner%20circle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyad%20Hamid%2C%20senior%20researcher%20at%20the%20Syrian%20Legal%20Development%20Programme%2C%20said%20that%20Russia%20has%20been%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20Assad's%20regime%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20supported%20Assad's%20regime%20for%20years%2C%20but%20the%20relationship%20deepened%20when%20Russian%20companies%20became%20involved%20in%20Syria's%20phosphate%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20between%20March%202018%20and%20September%202019%2C%20huge%20cash%20transfers%20took%20place%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20something%20that%20was%20unprecedented%20till%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20there%20is%20no%20record%20that%20Russian%20banks%20received%20currency%20notes%20worth%20%24250%20million%20within%20two%20years%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20happened%20because%20Assad's%20and%20his%20close%20associates%20seized%20personal%20control%20of%20critical%20parts%20of%20the%20devastated%20economy%20of%20war-torn%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssad%20and%20his%20aides%20also%20made%20money%20from%20international%20drug%20trafficking%20and%20fuel%20smuggling%2C%20the%20outlet%20said%2C%20quoting%20US%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734336240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ffelp57n8_hoarding-with-bashar-al-assad-photo_625x300_10_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbashar-al-assad-airlifted-250-million-of-syrias-wealth-to-moscow-report-7259512%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Assad%20fled%20Syria%20on%20December%208%20following%20an%2011-day%20rebel%20offensive%20led%20by%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbashar-al-assad-airlifted-250-million-of-syrias-wealth-to-moscow-report-7259512%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20mourns%20Zakir%20Hussain's%20demise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734336078000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116361119%2Cimgsize-62328.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpm-narendra-modi-mourns-ustad-zakir-hussains-demise-pays-tribute-to-him-he-brought-the-tabla-to-the-global-stage%2Farticleshow%2F116361117.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116