tro%20whose%20persona%20was%20as%20captivating%20as%20the%20magic%20his%20hands%20conjured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20the%20first%20memory%20of%20the%20legend%20is%20not%20a%20concert%20but%20the%201990s%20television%20advertisement%20for%20Brooke%20Bond%20Taj%20Mahal%20tea.%20The%20ad%20was%20not%20just%20marketing%20gold%20but%20a%20part%20of%20the%20shared%20memory%20of%20an%20entire%20generation.%20We%20still%20remember%20the%20maestro%20with%20Taj%20Mahal%20as%20his%20backdrop%20and%20the%20magical%20words%2C%20%26quot%3BWah%20Ustad%20nahi%2C%20wah%20Taj%20boliye%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20his%20long%20professional%20career%2C%20Ustad%20Zakir%20Hussain%20transcended%20every%20barrier%2C%20from%20class%20to%20country%20to%20language%20to%20religion.%20His%20tabla%20recreated%20the%20sound%20of%20rain%20and%20re-imagined%20the%20beats%20of%20Lord%20Shiva's%20Damru.%20And%20every%20time%20his%20long%2C%20curly%20hair%20swayed%20to%20the%20beats%2C%20we%20ignored%20his%20words%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWah%20Ustad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F_O9eOaNS3Lw%3Fsi%3DhkAiWNurJSQP2GXQ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Creation%20Of%20A%20Timeless%20Ad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201966%2C%20Brooke%20Bond%20Taj%20Mahal%20tea%20was%20launched%20in%20Kolkata.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20tabla%20maestro%20was%20not%20the%20first%20choice%20for%20the%20brand%20when%20it%20looked%20for%20celebrities%20for%20its%20ads.%20Actors%20Zeenat%20Aman%20and%20Malavika%20Tiwari%20appeared%20in%20Taj%20Mahal%20tea%20ads%20as%20the%20manufacturers%20tried%20to%20position%20it%20as%20an%20aspirational%20product.%20But%20by%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20makers%20observed%20that%20Taj%20Mahal%20tea%20was%20gaining%20popularity%20among%20the%20middle%20class%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindustan%20Thompson%20Associates%20(HTA)%20was%20roped%20in%20to%20craft%20a%20new%20brand%20image%20that%20would%20properly%20cater%20to%20the%20tea's%20expanded%20consumer%20base.%20Taj%20Mahal%20tea%20now%20needed%20a%20brand%20ambassador%20who%20balanced%20Indianness%20with%20Western%20exposure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fe9t9968NHZ8%3Fsi%3DX9pCNpQ9TXqi-EDx%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHTA's%20KS%20Chakravarthy%2C%20then%20a%20copywriter%2C%20was%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20tabla%20and%20identified%20Ustad%20Zakir%20Hussain%20as%20the%20best%20choice%20for%20the%20job.%20The%20maestro%20was%20approached%20and%20some%20reports%20say%20he%20was%20so%20delighted%20that%20he%20flew%20down%20from%20San%20Francisco%20to%20Agra%20at%20his%20own%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ad's%20script%20was%20simple%3A%20the%20maestro%20practises%20for%20hours%20to%20perfect%20his%20art%20and%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%20manufacturers%20of%20Taj%20Mahal%20tea%20tested%20numerous%20varieties%20to%20find%20the%20perfect%20blend%20and%20aroma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20economic%20reforms%20in%201991%2C%20cable%20TV%20reached%20Indian%20homes%20and%20the%20Ustad's%20smile%20beamed%20across%20our%20TV%20screens%2C%20lifting%20our%20mood%20and%20boosting%20the%20tea%20brand.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20most%20enduring%20ad%20campaigns%20ever%2C%20multiple%20faces%20appeared%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20including%20pop%20singer%20Alisha%20Chinai.%20But%20the%20Ustad%20remained%20constant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FMq6h6nCDZBw%3Fsi%3DP1eM2gVljn2m68QF%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20The%20Ustad%20Got%20Food%20As%20Fee%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%201998%20interview%20with%20Simi%20Garewal%2C%20Ustad%20Zakir%20Hussain%20said%20his%20mother%20Bavi%20Begam%20did%20not%20want%20him%20to%20be%20a%20tabla%20player.%20%26quot%3BAt%20my%20time%2C%20when%20we%20were%20very%20young%2C%20music%20was%20still%20not%20considered%20to%20be%20something%20you%20can%20make%20a%20decent%20living%20at.%20So%20my%20mother%20had%20seen%20me%20go%20to%20concerts%20and%20come%20back%20with%20packed%20food%20as%20payment.%20That%20was%20it.%20She%20wanted%20me%20to%20have%20a%20better%20life.%20So%20she%20really%20tried%20hard%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20studied%20and%20focused%20on%20being%20able%20to%20have%20something%20to%20fall%20back%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20maestro%20said%20his%20father%2C%20the%20legendary%20Ustad%20Alla%20Rakha%2C%20was%20his%20idol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ustad%20said%20he%20would%20often%20read%20letters%20inviting%20his%20father%20to%20perform.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20write%20back%20that%20he%20is%20not%20available%2C%20but%20his%20son%20is%20good%20enough.%20He%20would%20be%20glad%20to%20come%20and%20play.%20Many%20a%20times%20I%20arrived%20at%20the%20train%20station%20and%20they%20passed%20me%20by.%20They%20expected%20someone%20older%20and%20there%20was%20me%2C%20sometimes%20in%20school%20shorts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maestro%20recounted%20an%20incident%20in%20which%20he%20wanted%20to%20run%20away%20with%20a%20woman%20who%20worked%20at%20their%20place.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20one%20of%20the%20ladies%20who%20would%20look%20after%20us.%20I%20must%20have%20been%20very%20disgruntled%20with%20my%20mother%2C%20trying%20to%20stop%20me%20from%20playing%20music.%20I%20told%20Pujaran%2C%20let's%20just%20run%20away.%20She%20used%20to%20sing%20a%20bit.%20I%20told%20her%2C%20'you%20sing%2C%20I%20will%20play%2C%20we%20will%20make%20a%20living'.%20I%20packed%20my%20school%20bags%20and%20was%20ready%20to%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20maestro%20said%20he%20did%20not%20leave%20home%20because%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20I%20needed%20was%20there%2C%20my%20father%2C%20my%20teacher%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Jeans%20And%20Boombox%20Phase%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20was%20behind%20his%20decision%20to%20go%20to%20the%20US%20at%2018%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20wear%20jeans%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20rock%20and%20roll%20star.%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20million%20dollars.%20I%20walked%20around%20the%20streets%20of%20Bombay%20with%20a%20boombox%20on%20my%20shoulder%2C%20listening%20to%20Doors%20and%20Beatles%20and%20what%20not.%20I%20thought%20that%20was%20the%20way%20to%20go%2C%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20be%20famous%20very%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20when%20I%20got%20there%2C%20there%20was%20a%20whole%20different%20world%20altogether.%20I%20was%20living%20on%2025%20dollars%20a%20week%2C%20making%20one%20vegetable%20curry%20pot%2C%20heating%20it%20up%20every%20day%20and%20eating%20it%20with%20bread.%20Very%20tough%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0On%20his%20role%20in%20tabla's%20transcension%20from%20an%20accompaniment%20to%20an%20art%20form%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20contribution%20of%20mine%20has%20happened%20because%20of%20two%20generations%20of%20hard%20work.%20When%20people%20like%20I%20arrived%2C%20the%20groundwork%20was%20laid%2C%20tabla%20players%20were%20not%20non-entities%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20struggles%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20Indian%20classical%20music%20at%20one%20time%20was%20a%20second-class%20profession.%20And%20in%20that%20second-class%20profession%2C%20the%20tabla%20player%20was%20even%20lower%20on%20the%20ladder.%20At%20times%2C%20you%20didn't%20even%20know%20who%20was%20the%20tabla%20player%20on%20the%20record.%20I%20was%20playing%20with%20musicians%20who%20would%20not%20be%20known%2C%20and%20I%20would%20be%20the%20known%20person%2C%20but%20then%20I%20would%20have%20to%20give%20in%20because%20I%20was%20an%20accompanist%20and%20I%20had%20to%20take%20much%20less.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734335520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fn92oumkg_zakir-hussain-taj_625x300_16_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fustad-zakir-hussain-wah-taj-boliye-how-ustad-zakir-hussain-became-face-of-timeless-tea-ad-7258684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ustad%20Zakir%20Hussain%20has%20died%20at%2073.%20As%20curtains%20come%20down%20on%20a%20six-decade%20journey%20that%20catapulted%20tabla%20from%20an%20accompaniment%20to%20an%20art%20form%2C%20the%20country%20mourns%20the%20ever-smiling%2C%20wild-haired%20maestro%20whose%20persona%20was%20as%20captivating%20as%20his%20music%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fustad-zakir-hussain-wah-taj-boliye-how-ustad-zakir-hussain-became-face-of-timeless-tea-ad-7258684%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Indian%20teen%20rejected%20by%20Stanford%20is%20inspiring%20the%20internet%3A%20'Tough%20loss%2C%20but%20...%20'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734334961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116360495%2Cimgsize-1103223.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fhow-indian-teen-rejected-by-stanford-is-inspiring-the-internet-tough-loss-but-%2Farticleshow%2F116359947.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C