%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20lawyer%20Alex%20Shapiro%20has%20stated%20in%20a%20letter%20that%20Musk%20has%20faced%206%20years%20of%20harassment%20by%20the%20SEC%20and%20the%20Biden%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOh%20Gary%2C%20how%20could%20you%20do%20this%20to%20me%3F%20%F0%9F%A5%B9%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOoooQI77ZS%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOoooQI77ZS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1867357433493872874%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charges%20made%20by%20Musk%20and%20his%20lawyer%20are%20justified.%20The%20entire%20might%20of%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%20and%20the%20SEC%20as%20well%20as%20other%20departments%20came%20down%20on%20Musk%20and%20his%20companies.%20The%20deep%20rot%20in%20the%20system%20was%20exposed%20by%20Musk%20who%20has%20been%20under%20attack%20for%20various%20frivolous%20and%20false%20charges%20since%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20sign%20of%20a%20feud%20was%20visible%20in%20February%202021%2C%20barely%20a%20month%20after%20Joe%20Biden%20assumed%20office%20as%20the%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20%26quot%3BMy%20top%20recommendation%2C%20honestly%2C%20would%20be%20just%20add%20a%20carbon%20tax%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20billionaire%20owner%20of%20Tesla%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20Starlink%2C%20Neuralink%20and%20X.com%20told%20a%20podcaster.%20Musk%20lobbied%20for%20it%20with%20Biden%20in%20vain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202021%2C%20Biden%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Elon%20Musk%20was%20to%20be%20sidelined.%20A%20White%20House%20summit%20on%20electric%20vehicles%20was%20held%2C%20with%20the%20leadership%20of%20Ford%20and%20General%20Motors%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Auto%20Workers'%20Union%20UAW.%20Tesla%2C%20despite%20being%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20innovative%20company%20in%20the%20EV%20space%2C%20was%20not%20invited.%20Musk%20tweeted%20about%20it%20-%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20seems%20odd%20that%20Tesla%20wasn't%20invited.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EYeah%2C%20seems%20odd%20that%20Tesla%20wasn't%20invited%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1423156475799683075%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%205%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20comprehend%20why%20the%20Biden%20administration%20decided%20to%20%26quot%3Bcold%20shoulder%26quot%3B%20Tesla%20and%20Musk.%20Both%20men%20are%20pro-clean%20fuel%20and%20Musk%20had%20donated%20close%20to%20half%20a%20million%20dollars%20to%20Hillary%20Clinton's%20as%20well%20as%20Joe%20Biden's%20campaign.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20stated%20that%20he%20voted%20Democrat%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20present%20crisis%2C%20government%20is%20not%20the%20solution%20to%20our%20problem%3B%20Government%20is%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20former%20US%20President%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiF8h9j-b7ho%5C%22%3ERonald%20Reagan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20his%20inaugural%20address%20in%201981.%20His%20words%20find%20echo%20in%20what%20has%20happened%20to%20Elon%20Musk%20under%20the%20Biden%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20disaffection%20grew%2C%20Musk%20began%20criticising%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20policies.%20Biden%20then%20unleashed%20the%20full%20might%20of%20the%20government%20on%20Musk%20and%20his%20companies.%20They%20set%20up%20investigations%20into%20his%20companies%20and%20even%20forced%20Musk%20to%20agree%20to%20a%20clause%20wherein%20his%20tweets%20would%20be%20vetted%20by%20the%20Tesla%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20though%2C%20refused%20to%20kneel.%20In%20October%202022%2C%20he%20bought%20Twitter%2C%20the%20popular%20social%20media%20platform.%20He%20then%20released%20a%20series%20of%20internal%20documents%20that%20showed%20how%20deeply%20the%20Jack%20Dorsey-led%20team%20had%20been%20involved%20in%20censoring%20political%20views%20and%20content%2C%20thereby%20helping%20the%20Democrats.%20Musk%20handed%20over%20what%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20the%20Twitter%20Files%20to%20journalists%20Matt%20Taibbi%2C%20Bari%20Weiss%2C%20Lee%20Fang%2C%20Michael%20Shellenberger%2C%20David%20Zweig%20and%20Alex%20Berenson.%20The%20Twitter%20Files%20were%20published%20between%20December%202022%20to%20March%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administrated%20began%20to%20attack%20Musk's%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20U.S.%20Department%20of%20Transportation%20cited%20violations%20and%20fined%20SpaceX%20and%20Neuralink.%20A%20government%20body%20under%20the%20Department%20-%20the%20National%20Highway%20Traffic%20Safety%20Administration%20(NHTSA)%20-%20opened%20an%20investigation%20into%202.4%20million%20Tesla%20vehicles%20in%20December%202023%20for%20alleged%20safety%20issues%20with%20the%20company's%20Full%20Self-Driving%20software.%20This%20came%20on%20the%20back%20of%20four%20reported%20collisions%20and%20a%20fatal%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fe06bjqcg_national-highway-traffic-_625x300_16_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20was%20forced%20to%20recall%202%20million%20cars%20due%20to%20this%2C%20although%20it%20has%20provided%20evidence%20that%20its%20cars%20are%20safer%20with%20the%20autopilot%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collisions%20that%20the%20NHTSA%20is%20investigating%2