Hussain%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20Antonia%20Minnecola%2C%20a%20noted%20Kathak%20dancer%2C%20and%20their%20daughters%2C%20Anisa%20Qureshi%20and%20Isabella%20Qureshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20idiopathic%20pulmonary%20fibrosis%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdiopathic%20pulmonary%20fibrosis%20(IPF)%20is%20a%20chronic%20lung%20disease%20that%20affects%20the%20tissue%20around%20the%20air%20sacs%20(alveoli)%20in%20the%20lungs%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhlbi.nih.gov%2Fhealth%2Fidiopathic-pulmonary-fibrosis%C2%A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Institute%20of%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20occurs%20when%20this%20tissue%20thickens%20and%20stiffens%2C%20leading%20to%20permanent%20scarring%2C%20known%20as%20fibrosis%2C%20which%20makes%20breathing%20increasingly%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%26quot%3Bidiopathic%26quot%3B%20means%20the%20condition%20has%20no%20known%20cause%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F%C2%A0https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lung.org%2Flung-health-diseases%2Flung-disease-lookup%2Fidiopathic-pulmonary-fibrosis%C2%A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Lung%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIdiopathic%20pulmonary%20fibrosis%3A%20Symptoms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERisk%20factors%20for%20IPF%20include%20smoking%2C%20a%20family%20history%20of%20the%20condition%2C%20and%20older%20age.%20Common%20symptoms%20are%20shortness%20of%20breath%20and%20a%20persistent%20cough.%20While%20some%20people%20may%20not%20notice%20symptoms%20initially%2C%20these%20often%20worsen%20as%20the%20disease%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20progression%20of%20IPF%20varies%20widely%20%E2%80%93%20some%20people%20experience%20slow%20scarring%20over%20the%20years%2C%20while%20others%20see%20rapid%20worsening.%20Many%20patients%20face%20sudden%20flare-ups%2C%20called%20acute%20exacerbations%2C%20where%20symptoms%20become%20severe.%20Complications%20like%20pulmonary%20hypertension%20and%20respiratory%20failure%20can%20also%20occur%2C%20preventing%20the%20body%20from%20getting%20enough%20oxygen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIdiopathic%20pulmonary%20fibrosis%3A%20Treatments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20cure%20for%20IPF%2C%20but%20treatments%20can%20slow%20its%20progression%2C%20improve%20lung%20function%2C%20and%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20those%20living%20with%20the%20disease%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2Fidiopathic-pulmonary-fibrosis%2Ftreatment%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThere%2527s%2520currently%2520no%2520cure%2520for%2Cpalliative)%2520care%2520will%2520be%2520offered.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENHS%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you%20have%20IPF%2C%20taking%20care%20of%20yourself%20can%20help%20you%20stay%20as%20healthy%20as%20possible.%20Here%20are%20some%20tips%20according%20to%20the%20NHS%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuit%20smoking%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you%20smoke%2C%20stopping%20can%20greatly%20benefit%20your%20lungs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20active%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERegular%20exercise%20and%20maintaining%20fitness%20can%20improve%20your%20overall%20health.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEat%20well%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFollow%20a%20healthy%2C%20balanced%20diet%20to%20support%20your%20body.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20vaccinated%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEnsure%20you%20have%20the%20annual%20flu%20vaccine%20and%20the%20one-time%20pneumococcal%20vaccine%2C%20as%20lung%20infections%20can%20be%20more%20severe%20for%20those%20with%20IPF.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAvoid%20infections%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMinimise%20contact%20with%20people%20who%20have%20colds%20or%20chest%20infections.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%2