ds%20of%20the%20deceased%20woman%2C%20they%20could%20not%20help%20her%20identification.%20One%20blood-stained%20shirt%20and%20pant%20were%20found%20on%20the%20water%20body%20near%20the%20spot.%20It%20was%20found%20that%20both%20the%20wearing%20apparel%20had%20a%20tag%20of%20'New%20Star%20Tailors'%20stitched%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20clue%20was%20focused%20upon.%20Around%2010%20tailors%20with%20this%20name%20or%20similar%20name%20in%20Odisha%20were%20verified%20and%20their%20tag%20design%20was%20compared%20with%20the%20tag%20of%20the%20shirt%20and%20pant%20found%20at%20the%20spot.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20no%20match%20found.%20A%20tailor%20in%20Ganjam%20district%20informed%20that%20such%20kind%20of%20tags%20are%20being%20used%20in%20Gujarat%2C%26quot%3B%20DCP%20Meena%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DCP%20said%20the%20Gujarat%20police%20was%20contacted%20and%20they%20found%20such%20a%20tailor%20in%20Surat.%20The%20tailor's%20tag%20had%20a%20number%20'3833'%20which%20was%20matched%20and%20upon%20search%2C%20it%20was%20seen%20that%20the%20shirt%20was%20stitched%20for%20one%20person%20named%20'Babu'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20other%20detail%20available.%20However%2C%20the%20tailor%20gave%20one%20important%20clue%20that%20he%20had%20to%20return%20Rs%20100%20to%20the%20customer%20'babu'%20but%20he%20did%20not%20have%20the%20change.%20So%2C%20he%20transferred%20Rs%20100%20on%20the%20e-wallet%20of%20one%20mobile%20number.%20That%20number%20was%20contacted%20and%20it%20was%20found%20that%20he%20is%20a%20friend%20of%20'babu'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDetails%20of%20'Babu'%20were%20received.%20He%20was%20found%20to%20be%20Jaganath%20Duhuri%20(27)%20%40%20Babu%20%40%20Bapi%20of%20Kendrapada.%20It%20was%20found%20that%20he%20(Babu)%20was%20going%20back%20to%20Surat%20by%20train.%20The%20train%20was%20passing%20through%20Rayagada%20when%20he%20was%20nabbed%2C%26quot%3B%20DCP%20Meena%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20further%20verification%20and%20interrogation%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20he%20was%20the%20brother-in-law%20of%20the%20deceased.%20He%20also%20revealed%20that%20he%20committed%20crime%20with%20the%20help%20of%20his%20brother%20Balaram%20Duhuri%20and%20cousin%20Hapi%20Duhuri.%20All%20three%20have%20been%20apprehended%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBalaram%20Duhuri%20was%20the%20husband%20of%20the%20deceased%20woman.%20The%20motive%20of%20the%20crime%20is%20chronic%20marital%20dispute%20between%20the%20deceased%20and%20her%20husband.%20Balaram%20was%20doubting%20that%20the%20deceased%20was%20having%20an%20extra-marital%20affair%20with%20someone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DCP%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734330000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fj1hggulg_odisha-police-generic-_625x300_24_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftailors-tag-on-shirt-helps-police-to-crack-mysterious-cuttack-murder-case-7258721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20tailor's%20tag%20on%20a%20blood-stained%20shirt%20found%20near%20the%20crime%20scene%20helped%20the%20Odisha%20Police%20to%20crack%20a%20mysterious%20murder%20case%20and%20arrest%20three%20people%2C%20an%20officer%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftailors-tag-on-shirt-helps-police-to-crack-mysterious-cuttack-murder-case-7258721%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Final%20Hours!%20IKS%20IPO%20closes%20today%3A%20Subscription%20zooms%204x%2C%20GMP%20up%2030%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734329957000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Ffinal