ing%20water.%20They%20are%20ideal%20for%20forest%20patrolling%20in%20shallow%20waters%20and%20marshlands%2C%20as%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20stuck%20in%20the%20mud.%20They%20offer%20an%20affordable%20option%20for%20fishermen%20and%20can%20function%20as%20small%20ferries%20or%20water%20taxis.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20could%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20eco-tourism%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20elaborates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20commercial%20production%20has%20yet%20to%20begin%2C%20the%20company%20has%20received%20inquiries%20from%20abroad%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734319800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-4-1733814775.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D387876%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Northeast%20India%20has%20become%20a%20hub%20for%20creativity%20and%20innovation%2C%20with%20local%20ventures%20offering%20unique%2C%20eco-friendly%20solutions%20to%20everyday%20challenges.%20These%20innovations%2C%20from%20sustainable%20storage%20units%20to%20eco-conscious%20products%2C%20reflect%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20rich%20cultural%20heritage%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20develop%20practical%2C%20low-cost%20technologies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Aruna%20Raghuram%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F387876%2Fnortheast-india-ecofriendly-innovations-soy-wax-candle-longpi-jar-bamboo-boat-banana-fibre-cold-storage%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Legendary%20Indian%20tabla%20player%20Zakir%20Hussain%20dies%20at%2073%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734318485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3c8f%2Flive%2Ff1bb4480-bb59-11ef-b3c2-275d2a9f89f1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc2