l%20shadow.%20%E2%80%9CSaleya%20is%20one%20of%20our%20success%20stories.%20She%20is%20not%20only%20practising%20the%20usage%20of%20sanitary%20pads%20regularly%20but%20also%20inspiring%20over%20a%20hundred%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mrinal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoma%20personally%20wants%20every%20woman%20and%20girl%20to%20use%20sanitary%20napkins.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20buy%20sanitary%20napkins%20on%20our%20own%2C%20but%20if%20SEED%20can%20continue%20to%20provide%20us%20with%20more%2C%20it%20would%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20asserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrinal%20informs%20that%20today%2C%20Saleya%20and%20several%20other%20women%20in%20her%20locality%20have%20also%20taken%20to%20wall%20graffiti%20to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20menstruation%20and%20menstrual%20hygiene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20say%20that%20we%20have%20achieved%20100%25%20success%20in%20all%20areas%20we%20have%20intervened%2C%20but%20yes%2C%20over%2070%25%20of%20households%20have%20stopped%20the%20practices%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20health%20issues.%20Some%20taboos%20still%20exist%20and%20we%20have%20to%20continue%20working%20towards%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20Mrinal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20challenges%2C%20emphasising%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrinal%20acknowledges%20that%20the%20current%20measures%20are%20temporary%20solutions%20and%20require%20sustained%20funding%20and%20innovative%20approaches.%20He%20highlights%20the%20ongoing%20challenge%20of%20affordable%20sanitary%20pads.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20they%20are%20implementing%20a%20programme%20that%20empowers%20rural%20women%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F321703%2Fiit-material-scientists-innovate-biodegradable-super-absorbent-sheets-for-sanitary-pads%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduce%20sanitary%20pads%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20a%20du