d%20Nikon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20gave%20Jijo%20an%20inclination%20towards%20photography%20and%20inspired%20him%20to%20begin%20experimenting%20with%20motorsports%20photography.%20Bigrock%20Dirtpark%20(India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20off-road%20training%20facility)%20appointed%20him%20as%20the%20official%20photographer%20for%20their%20XTREME%20ENDURO%202024%20race%20after%20years%20of%20working%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20like%20going%20to%20work%2C%20making%20new%20friends%20and%20clicking%20good%20pictures%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jijo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJijo%E2%80%99s%20talent%20soon%20caught%20the%20eye%20of%C2%A0%20Ultraviolette%20CEO%C2%A0%20Narayan%20Subramaniam.%20Aniket%2C%20a%20motorcycle%20designer%2C%20who%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Ultraviolette%20team%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20started%20accompanying%20me%20on%20various%20projects%20and%20eventually%20collaborating%20with%20Ultraviolette%20Automotive%20on%20special%20projects%20where%20I%20was%20working.%E2%80%9D%20Narayan%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20philosophy%20prioritising%20passion%20over%20academic%20qualifications%2C%20encouraged%20Jijo%E2%80%99s%20creativity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhotographing%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20F77%20Mach%202%20motorcycle%20showcased%20Jijo%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20capture%20moments%20with%20enthusiasm.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20my%20pictures%20to%20show%20the%20excitement%20of%20the%20launch%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jijo%20says%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20Ultraviolette%2C%20we%20believe%20diversity%20in%20talent%20and%20perspective%20drives%20us%20forward%2C%20and%20Jijo%20is%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20this.%20His%20dedication%20and%20commitment%20remind%20us%20of%20resilience%20and%20determination.%20We%E2%80%99re%20proud%20to%20have%20him%20as%20a%20valued%20member%20of%20our%20Ultraviolette%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20Narayan%20shar