live%20with%20the%20vibrant%20activity%20of%20hundreds%20of%20avian%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEstablished%20in%201798%20by%20the%20British%2C%20Vedanthangal%20is%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20bird%20sanctuaries.%20Located%20in%20Chengalpattu%20district%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20it%20spans%20over%2074%20acres%20and%20is%20home%20to%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20birds%2C%20both%20resident%20and%20migratory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sanctuary%20is%20meticulously%20managed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment%20and%20Forests%2C%20with%20efforts%20rooted%20in%20local%20conservation%20practices%20that%20date%20back%20over%20250%20years.%20Recognised%20internationally%20as%20an%20Important%20Bird%20and%20Biodiversity%20Area%20(IBA)%2C%20the%20community%20understands%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20this%20unique%20ecosystem%2C%20where%20bird%20droppings%20help%20fertilise%20surrounding%20agricultural%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202693px)%20100vw%2C%202693px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvedanthangal-bird4_11zon-1731664993.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222693%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20flock%20of%20Asian%20Openbill%20spotted%20in%20Vedanthangal%20Bird%20Sanctuary.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvedanthangal-bird4_11zon-1731664993.jpg%202693w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvedanthangal-bird4_11zon-1731664993-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvedanthangal-bird4_11zon-1731664993-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvedanthangal-bird4_11zon-1731664993-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fvedanthangal-bird4_11zon-1731664993-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2